headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Hunting Pack (Remix)
content:
Drive a vehicle that’s rigged to explode if its speed dips beneath the threshold, avoid opponents ramming you while your teammates try to provide some assistance, and make it to the checkpoint to emerge victorious in Hunting Pack (Remix) — paying out Double Rewards this week.

Winning one round of Hunting Pack (Remix) will also unlock the Trade Price for the Declasse Scramjet from Warstock Cache & Carry.
